---
<link rel="canonical" href="https://cayadservices.com/why-us/our-team/" />

<style>
  .custom-background {
    background:
      linear-gradient(hsla(250, 75%, 5%, 0.5), rgba(6, 3, 21, 0.5)),
      url("/img/how.webp") center center no-repeat;
    background-size: cover;
  }
</style>

